The stem {{term||tul-|lang=la}}, related to {{m|la|tollō}}, is from {{etyl|ine-pro|la}} {{m|ine-pro|*telh₂-||to bear, support, suffer}}, whence also English {{term|thole||to endure|lang=en}}. The stem of {{m|la|lātus}} has the same source, reduced from {{m|la|*tlātus}}.

